"""Test that giving bad units to a time history results in a validation error
        """
assert not v.validate({'datapoints': [{'time-histories': [time_history]}]},
    update=True)
pytest.mark.parametrize('time_history', [('pressure', 'candela*ampere'), (
    'volume', 'candela*ampere'), ('temperature', 'candela*ampere'), (
    'piston position', 'candela*ampere'), ('light emission',
    'candela*ampere'), ('OH emission', 'candela*ampere'), ('absorption',
    'candela*ampere')], indirect=['time_history'])
